**[1842, 09-23] Ms.A.9.2.20.66**

Bird, Mark Baker, to Chapmans; Cap Haytien. Statistics of the Wesleyan
Mission in Hayti, naming stations, missionaries, number of schools, etc.
2 p.

[The cover note is written by an S. or J. Bird., the statistics by M.B.
Bird. The cover note includes:] “We rejoice with you in the success of
the cause which lays near your heart. May it prosper more and more ‘till
all the nations see that man should [?] be & form one family the wide
world over’.”


